title: About
text:
My name is Tayyibah Shah. I am a student at the University of Sheffield and am currently on exchange at the National University of Singapore. I study Digital Media and Sociology.
I chose this module to develop my coding skills in order to broaden my skillset. Coding is an important skill and therefore will broaden my career opportunities.
